reviewText: Most odd this video I already got.

i gave this product a two because some of the footage is a rehash of another product that I bought on Amazon, I did not learn hardly anything new about helicopters. I was hoping for a documentary that showed more combat footage, though the color footage is of good quality. I would recommend this to someone that would like a packet of reasonably priced dvds on military helicopters but has not purchased a good variety of dvds on helicopters!
